    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1866-07-03T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1866-07-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="376" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d376">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Prevost</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-07-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 3, 1866</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have to acknowledge the receipt of your
                            despatch No. 16, of June 10th last, communicating your action with
                            regard to the instalment due from the government of Ecuador, under the
                            convention of November, 1862.</p>
                <p>Your proceedings in the premises are approved, and you will in future be
                            guided by the same instructions which moved your action in this
                            matter.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">L. V. Prevost,</hi> Esq., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
